                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "37678f63becb4df2b1e50",
                    "stepText": "Finally, after substituting the known numerical values (with $!$U_{initial} = 0.25 \\text{ J}$!$ and the friction force calculated as $!$f = 0.98 \\text{ N}$!$) into the conservation equation, you obtain a quadratic equation in $!$x_m$!$. Which of the following is the correct quadratic formula to solve for $!$x_m$!$?",
